OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDriest for the far north of
OL,6,FScotland, though chilly. Wet across
OL,7,Fnortheast England and southern
OL,8,FScotland as rain slowly eases.
OL,9,FScattered showers elsewhere, some
OL,10,Fheavy with hail and thunder over
OL,11,Fsouthern England and Wales, and
OL,12,Ffeeling rather humid here.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers gradually decaying
OL,15,Fovernight and then mainly dry but
OL,16,Frather cloudy, though rain reaching
OL,17,Fthe Northern Isles by dawn. Chilly in
OL,18,Fthe north with patchy rural frost;
OL,19,Fmilder further south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
