OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FRain slowly moving across
OL,6,Fnorthern Scotland. Rather cloudy for
OL,7,Fcentral and southern areas with
OL,8,Foccasional showers, heavy in the
OL,9,Fsouthwest. Mostly dry elsewhere with
OL,10,Fsome sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
